tora-san 's island encounter ( 男はつらいよ &lt;unk&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : torajirō yori ai o o &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1984 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and keiko kishi as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san 's island encounter is tora-san 's first entry in the popular , long-running otoko wa tsurai yo series .